Title: Trump’s $7 billion meme coin hasn’t made him richer, Forbes and Bloomberg say
Notes:
Classic pump and dump. $Trump and $Melania coins. 
While some reports said that Trump had added tens of billions of dollars to his fortune through the meme coin issuance, “those numbers are based on theoretical prices for crypto assets that Trump cannot sell right now, which is why Forbes values them at zero, in keeping with our methodology of generally excluding unsellable assets from net worth tallies,” Forbes’s Dan Alexander, a journalist who has extensively covered Trump’s business interests for years, wrote.

Notes: Project 2025 is a political initiative published in April 2023 by the American conservative think tank The Heritage Foundation.
